[
  {
    "text": "日々の暮らしの織物",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.09987810123318035,
      "left": 0.35296031617567253,
      "width": 0.29404398938174503,
      "height": 0.025246211069286623
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "朝の日差しが静かな通りを優しく照らし、温かな",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.15505268267341019,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.3593868957688051,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "光が木々の間を通り抜けて地面に美しい影を落と",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.17399207582366275,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.3593868957688051,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "しています。鳥たちが木の上で優しく歌い、その",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.19293146897391528,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.3567731923237879,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "心地よいさえずりが眠っていた街を目覚",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.21187086212416784,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.2917568037337847,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "め",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.21187086212416784,
      "left": 0.40940384053954515,
      "width": 0.016335784327308006,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "させ、",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.21187086212416784,
      "left": 0.4257396077510451,
      "width": 0.04900731875030754,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "新しい一",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.23081025527442037,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.06534308596180761,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "日が希望と可能性に満ちた始まりを迎え",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.23081025527442037,
      "left": 0.18299012276756813,
      "width": 0.2940438269228056,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "ます。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.24974964842467293,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.04737374945562801,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "技術の進歩は前例のないスピードで私たちの生活",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.28099964712258946,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.3579166665408491,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "様式と働き方を根本的に変えています。人工知能",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.29993904027284196,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.3564464746903424,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "から再生可能エネルギーまで、毎",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3188784334230945,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.24438309002141503,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "日新しい革新と",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3188784334230945,
      "left": 0.36203012682717556,
      "width": 0.11435038759630707,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "発明",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3378178265733471,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.032671551538807846,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "が現れ、これらの技術的進歩は社会のあらゆ",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3378178265733471,
      "left": 0.15031858834456835,
      "width": 0.32671536134580537,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "る側面に深い影響を与え、私たちが世界と関わる",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.35675721972359953,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.3593868957688051,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "方法を再構築しています。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3756966128738521,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.1934155015813392,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "古代文明は驚くべき記念碑と建築の奇跡を建設",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.40694661157176876,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.34174425814607184,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "し、これらの壮大な構造物は何千年もの時を経て",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4258860047220212,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.3593868957688051,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "も堂々と立ち続けています。エ",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.44482539787227376,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.2270671887821267,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "ジプトのピラミッ",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.44482539787227376,
      "left": 0.34471422558788717,
      "width": 0.13068617343525718,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "ドから中国の万里の長",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4637647910225263,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.16335768923080685,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "城まで、これらの建築物は",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4637647910225263,
      "left": 0.2810047260365674,
      "width": 0.19537578838691524,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "先祖の卓越した知恵と驚くべき創",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.48270418417277877,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.24372965487707288,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "造性を示すだけ",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.48270418417277877,
      "left": 0.3613766916828334,
      "width": 0.11435038759630703,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "でなく、人類文明の輝かしい歴史の証人でもあり",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5016435773230313,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.3593868957688051,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "ます。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5205829704732838,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.04737374945562801,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "教育は社会の進歩と個人の成長",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5527799388287131,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.22870075807680643,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "を推進する根本的",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5527799388287131,
      "left": 0.3463477948825669,
      "width": 0.13068615480780685,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "な基礎です。体系的な学習と継続的な知識の蓄積",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5717193319789656,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.3577533077241262,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "を通じて、人々は自分たちの生活と周囲のコ",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5906587251292182,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.3260619260789142,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "ミュ",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5906587251292182,
      "left": 0.4437089628846748,
      "width": 0.03267155153880782,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "ニティを改善するために必要な様々な道具、技",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6095981182794707,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.3425610521071368,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "能、そして深い洞察を獲得し、より良い未来の構",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6285375114297233,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.3584067429910173,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "築に貢献することができます。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6474769045799758,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.2270671887821267,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "自",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6787269032778924,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.016335784327307982,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "然は比類のない美しい景観と生命を維持するた",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6787269032778924,
      "left": 0.13398282113306847,
      "width": 0.3430511285573053,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "めに不可欠な貴重な資源を惜しみなく提供してく",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.697666296428145,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.3577533077241262,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "れます。清らかな空気から純粋な水、肥沃な土壌",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7166056895783975,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.3577533077241262,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "から多様な生物まで、環境",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.73554508272865,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.19537578838691544,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "を保護し大切にするこ",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.73554508272865,
      "left": 0.313022825192676,
      "width": 0.16335768923080665,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "とは、私たちの世代の責任であり、未来の子孫が",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7544844758789027,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.3593868957688051,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "地球の素晴らしさ",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7734238690291552,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.1306861548078071,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "を享受し続けるための鍵となり",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7734238690291552,
      "left": 0.24833319161356765,
      "width": 0.22821068162663785,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "ます。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7923632621794077,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.04737374945562801,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "効果的なコ",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.8236132608773243,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.08167885317330749,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "ミュニケーションは異なる文",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.8236132608773243,
      "left": 0.19932588997906797,
      "width": 0.2123649908653064,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "、民",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.8236132608773243,
      "left": 0.4280266309400661,
      "width": 0.032671551538807915,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "化",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.8236132608773243,
      "left": 0.4116908637285663,
      "width": 0.016335784327308006,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "族、国家の間に理解と協力の重要な橋を架けま",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.8425526540275767,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.3430511285573054,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "す。言語は人類の最も偉大な発明の一つとして、",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.8614920471778293,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.3561197571794459,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "地理的・文",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.15505268267341019,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.08167885317330735,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "的な境界を",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.15505268267341019,
      "left": 0.6176224247559272,
      "width": 0.08167885317330735,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "越えて、お互いの考え、",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.15505268267341019,
      "left": 0.6993012608134265,
      "width": 0.1777331507641817,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "化",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.15505268267341019,
      "left": 0.6012866575444272,
      "width": 0.016335784327308006,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "を",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.17399207582366275,
      "left": 0.6012866575444272,
      "width": 0.016335784327308006,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "経験、知恵",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.17399207582366275,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.08167885317330735,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "共有することを可能にし、相互理",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.17399207582366275,
      "left": 0.6176224247559272,
      "width": 0.24503652528830566,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "解、尊重、信頼の関係を",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.19293146897391528,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.17969345644230642,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "築くことができます。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.19293146897391528,
      "left": 0.6993012608134265,
      "width": 0.16172410130867693,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "科学研究は厳密な方法と絶え間ない探求を通じ",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.22418146767183195,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.34305112855730474,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "て、宇宙に隠された謎と法則を徐々に明",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.24312086082208448,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.2933903916559143,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "らかにし",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.24312086082208448,
      "left": 0.8129981960270342,
      "width": 0.06534308596180735,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "ています。それぞれの新しい発見は未知の世界へ",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.262060253972337,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
