      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "の扉を開",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.28099964712258946,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.06534308596180763,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "くようなものであり、同時により多くの",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.28099964712258946,
      "left": 0.5849508903329275,
      "width": 0.2935537504726369,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "魅力的な問題をもたらし、科学者たちがさらに広",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.29993904027284196,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.35938689576880484,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "大な未知の領域を探求し続ける動機となっていま",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3188784334230945,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.35758994890740287,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "す。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3378178265733471,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.031037982244128105,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "芸術はその独",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.37001479492877626,
