      "width": 0.09801462038480707,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "特な方法で、言葉の制限を超",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.37001479492877626,
      "left": 0.6176224247559272,
      "width": 0.21171155559841495,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "えた深",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.37001479492877626,
      "left": 0.829333963238534,
      "width": 0.04900731875030745,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "い感情と抽象的な思想を表現し伝えます。絵画、",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3880072184215162,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.35775334510157525,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "音楽、彫刻、文学など、これらの創",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.40694661157176876,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.2613722924998056,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "造性に富んだ",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.40694661157176876,
      "left": 0.7809800968709256,
      "width": 0.09801462038480735,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "芸術作品は人々の想像力と創",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4258860047220212,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.21236499086530605,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "造力を刺激するだけ",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4258860047220212,
      "left": 0.7319727952364261,
      "width": 0.1470219220193069,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "でなく、既存の概念に挑戦し、私たちがこの複雑",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.44482539787227376,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.35938689576880484,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "で多彩な世界を新しい視点から理解する手助けを",
